National Realty L.P. said it sold its common stock holdings in four affiliated entities to American Realty Trust Inc. for $8.7 million. 

American Realty Trust purchased all of National Realty's holdings in four real estate investment trusts -- about 1,130,000 shares of Continental Mortgage & Equity Trust, 56,000 shares of Income Opportunity Realty Trust, 1,020,000 shares of National Income Realty Trust, and 217,000 shares of Transcontinental Realty Investors. 

National Realty L.P. is a national real estate investment company.
American Realty Trust Inc. is a real estate investment trust.
Both are affiliates of Southmark Corp. 

